    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1920-01-28T07:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1920-01-28T07:00:00-05:00" n="937"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d937">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">860j.01/193: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in France</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Wallace</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Paris</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1920-01-28T12:00:00+00:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">January 28, 1920—noon</hi>
                        </date>.<lb/>[Received 1:40 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>280. Mission. Your 197, January 26, 7 p.m.,<note n="23" xml:id="d937fn23">Not
                        printed.</note> received this morning. Formal notification to Armenian
                    Delegation of action of Council granting <hi rend="italic">de facto</hi>
                    recognition was made yesterday by M. Mil-lerand as reported in my 276, January
                    27, 7 p.m.<note n="23" xml:id="d937fn24">Not printed.</note>
                </p>
                <p>I have requested Foreign Office to inform Armenian Delegation immediately that
                    there has been a misunderstanding and that American participation in action
                    taken should be canceled.</p>
                <p>In view of what has occurred request Department’s specific approval of this
                    action and further instructions if any are deemed necessary.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Wallace</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
